          h1 Overview
          p I designed the wedding materials for my own wedding. I actually wanted to avoid designing our materials. Because I didn’t want to deal with a bridezilla. Even worse… my bridezilla. I decided to make the materials when I saw what other designers were charging for templates and services. The thought of creating my own pieces from scratch with cheap fonts and stock photos brought me to the realization that I might as well do it myself.
          p To be honest I was surprised by how easy it was to find the proper resources. I was even more surprised by how my soon to be wife was on board with the creative direction.
