        .col-1-2
          h2 Invitation
          p I found two other illustrations from the that matched the theme of the save the date. One male tiger and a female tiger. They represented Meagan and I were the first illustration represented that I love was like the eye of tiger. I used the same type and color treatment for the sake of consistency and cost reduction. As part of the invitations we sent out. We included a self addressed post card. I wanted to create a fun way for our guests to send their response back. The idea to use a flowchart came from Wired Magazine. I always love looking to see what all the options for answers could be. So I included a chart the told us how excited our friends and family were to attend or not make it.
          h2 A happy wife makes for a happy designer
          p I was surprised how much fun this project would be. I was even more surprised by how well the collateral was received. I had a lot of people who were excited to come and loved the fact that they had never seen an invite like ours.
